Italy Government Ministers Reject Draft Law on Solar, Commerzbank Says

-- B y   M a r c   R o c a
-- 
2011-03-03T11:16:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-03/italy-government-ministers-reject-draft-law-on-solar-commerzbank-says.html
Italian policymakers have rejected a
draft regulation that would have capped solar installations in
the country at 8 gigawatts, Ben Lynch, an analyst at
Commerzbank, wrote in a note to clients today.  The note cited unidentified contacts. It said the
government will continue to debate whether to scale back
incentives for the industry.  To contact the reporter on this story:
